-- Samsung sees rise in 2008 digital media sales
-- 
-- Tue Jan 8, 2008 1:41am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/01/08/us-samsung-electronics-digitalmedia-idUSSEL00026320080108

 

 SEOUL  (Reuters) - Samsung Electronics ( 005930.KS ) said on Tuesday it is targeting a 15 percent rise to 30 trillion won ($32 billion) in global sales of digital media this year from 2007 through steady growth in TV, printers and computers. 

 Park Jong-woo, who leads the business, also said in a statement that the company's global pre-tax profit for the digital media department topped 1 trillion won in 2007 for the first time. (Reporting by Kim Yeon-hee; Editing by Sei Chong)